docs/architecture.md — the "DB-aware extraction executor (R6 + R7, landed)" pseudo-code block needs steps 2 and 3 reordered to show the snapshot load BEFORE the decide call.
HANDOFF.md — architectural rule 8 ("Advisory-locked, race-safe promotion") gets a sentence noting that the candidate + evidence are now also re-read inside the lock, not just the hash.
