Migrate claim-extraction.ts to the new shape; verify pre-push gate.
Migrate document-ingestion.ts to the new shape; verify pre-push gate.
Remove the legacy decision and snapshotInputs fields from ExecutePromotionInput.
Update the 4 docs in the same commit as step 4.
The migration-then-cleanup sequence keeps each step trivially typecheckable and means we never have a broken half-state.

